{'title': 'Reddinator Widget for Reddit', 'description': 'Reddinator is a Widget & App for Reddit.\r\nIt\'s built to be easy to use, highly customisable and completely optimised to make you spend every waking moment on Reddit.\r\n\r\nIf you love having Reddit at your fingertips then this is the App for you. \r\n\r\nScroll down below for an overview of the awesome.\r\n\r\nReddinator is proudly an open source project, if you would like to contribute please visit:\r\nhttp://github.com/micwallace/reddinator\r\n\r\nFeatures:\r\nâ€¢ All Widgets are independently customisable, allowing you to pick a built-in or custom theme for each widget.\r\nâ€¢ "Load more" button at the bottom of all feeds, allowing you to Reddit till your hearts content\r\nâ€¢ Seamless account integration keeps your Subreddits & Multis at your fingertips\r\nâ€¢ Search & subscribe to new Subreddits & unsubscribe from the stale ones\r\nâ€¢ Search for posts\r\nâ€¢ Domain subreddits (view posts from a domain)\r\nâ€¢ Create & Edit Multireddits\r\nâ€¢ Get notified of new messages via indicators & notifications.\r\nâ€¢ Access messages, account history, saved & hidden posts straight from the app.\r\nâ€¢ Reddinator View combines the items content, Reddit comments page and voting buttons into a tabbed layout.  Read the article and participate in Reddits great community discussion at the same time!\r\nâ€¢ Choose default click action for feed items. You can open in the tabbed "Reddinator View", the item\'s content page or open the item\'s Reddit page in the web browser.\r\nâ€¢ Vote for posts quickly and easily, including from the widget.\r\nâ€¢ Use the post option dialogue to quickly hide, save and perform other useful functions for each post\r\n(Click on the cogs icon in a post widget or long press on a post within the app)\r\nâ€¢ Vote & reply to posts, comments and messages\r\n\r\nGlobal options:\r\nâ€¢ Feed Item click action (as listed above)\r\nâ€¢ Initial feed items to load\r\nâ€¢ Widget Auto-refresh interval